Koemei module for Kaltura MediaSpace (KMS)
============

Version 0.3.2

Installation and usage
--------

A user guide on how to install and use the Koemei KMS module: https://docs.google.com/document/d/10EaHXiGB1r5-saE83OeaVZ0Sda-HlZofClo_CDKP0t0/edit?usp=sharing

Known issues
--------

* readonly view should be like on the classpage
* when editing the transcript, closing the edit window will close also the readonly transcript
* authorization on publish
* problem when saving a transcript: Probably some problem with authorization (regular user can create a caption but not edit it...)
