* the improve caption button does not display in the edit
* publish should not be auto....
* delay
* webm format support

Troubleshooting
--------

* In case your newly added media files are not automatically transcribed, please check that the notifications are enabled in KMC (Settings>Integration Settings>Notifications) and that the url is https://www.koemei.com/REST/services/notify/kaltura
* Please contact support@koemei.com if you need help setting up or using this plugin.

Revision history
--------

0.1.0 : Initial version
0.1.1 : RC - Fixes to 0.1.0 following comments from Kaltura R&D validation team
0.1.2 : Repository refactoring (removed uncompressed KMS source)
0.2.0 : KMS5 compatibility
0.2.1 : KMS5 compatibility - fixes for 20130827 review
0.2.2 : KMS5 compatibility - fixes for 20130904 review
0.3.0 : KMS5 compatibility - fixes for 20131030 review
* use latest widget version (3.2) - performance improvement on longer videos
* UI fix - button margin
* JS fix - declare all variables
0.3.1 : compatibility with KMS version 5.4.03
0.3.2 : move repository to github

